      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help, but they don't get it. they think there's just some \"spark\" i can relight if i try hard enough. but it's not a spark. it's like the person who used to live here just... left. i'm just the leftovers. a shell. how can you \"find your way back\" to someone who doesn't exist anymore? it feels more like i'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up to the emptiness.",
